# graphify scope for the MyHospital workspace knowledge graph.
#
# Current graph scope:
# - docs/ and specs/
# - root harness docs (AGENTS.md, CLAUDE.md)
# - Linux migration tooling docs/scripts in scripts/
# - non-secret Claude hook/settings files
#
# The graph maps design intent, specs, and harness/tooling rules. It should not
# mix in FE/BE source code graphs, generated artifacts, secrets, caches, or
# runtime output.

myhospital-fe/**
!myhospital-fe/
!myhospital-fe/CLAUDE.md
myhospital-be/**
!myhospital-be/
!myhospital-be/CONVENTIONS.md
!myhospital-be/.claude/
!myhospital-be/.claude/settings.local.json

agent-tools/
mcps/
terminals/
.playwright-mcp/
.serena/

worktrees/
trash/
_db-backups/
.harness-backups/
.linux-migration-backups/
.obsidian/

# Deprecated PowerShell archive — must never enter a "design intent" graph.
scripts/legacy-powershell/
*.ps1

graphify-out/cache/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.log
*.tmp
*.bak-linux-migration

# Secrets, auth, and runtime capture artifacts. The Windows-built graph leaked
# session-auth / cookie / token / .har content; keep these out of every rebuild.
